{"word":"ἀνακλίνω","slug":"ἀνακλίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀναϰλίνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνά\">ἀνά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κλίνω\">κλίνω</a></el>] ‘cause to recline’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of an infant <b><i>lay, lay down</i> <a href='B:490 2:7'>Lk 2:7</a>;</b> of guests for a meal <b><i>make to recline</i> <a href='B:480 6:39'>Mk 6:39</a>; <a href='B:490 12:37'>Lk 12:37</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> <i>recline</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b><a href='B:470 8:11'>Mt 8:11</a>; <a href='B:470 14:19'>14:19</a>; <a href='B:470 20:28'>20:28</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:480 6:39'>Mk 6:39</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:490 7:36'>Lk 7:36</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνακεφαλαιόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνακόπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}